txt.en: 'The Lady of the Wood is very mysterious. I do not know her purposes.'
'Aragorn is a doughty Man. When we come to Minas Tirith, he will be a great help to my people.'
'I am ready to leave this place.'
'The halflings are too trusting of these Elves.'
'Legolas has proven himself a useful companion, but I am not sure of these other Elves.'
